  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, NameTag, NBSwitch, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject

    public class NBSwitchImpl
extends NameTagImpl
implements NBSwitch
    An implementation of the model object 'NB Switch'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Substation
    • From NB Node
    • To NB Node
    • Switch Type
    • Normal Status
    • Xpu
    • Name Rating
